Session Class

class aiont.Session(*, session: Optional[aiohttp.client.ClientSession] = None)

First-class interface for making HTTP requests to Nitro Type.

async get_racer(username: str, *, session: Optional[aiohttp.client.ClientSession] = None) → Optional[aiont.Racer]

Get a racer with a username.

Parameters

  • username (str) – The racer’s username.

  • session (aiohttp.ClientSession or None) – The aiohttp session to use.

Raises

aiont.HTTPException – Getting the racer failed.

Return type

Optional[aiont.Racer]
